    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH1a0904-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.93" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:07:40.859+09:00">And so the ministers from the older generation in his own family will be earnestly prepared to die for the ancestral temple,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.94" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:08:19.845+09:00">the ministers in charge of the legal system will earnestly ready to die for the Altars of State,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.95" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:09:09.681+09:00">the domestic ministers will be earnestly ready to serve their ruler;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.96" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:10:08.389+09:00">the defense ministers will be earnestly ready to die for the city walls and the borders of the land.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.97" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:10:30.585+09:00">That is why it is said that the sage has golden city walls,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.98" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:10:41.853+09:00">that alludes to this meaning.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.99" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:11:12.302+09:00">These men are ready to die for one</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.100" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:11:34.422+09:00">and as a result one can survive together with them;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.101" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:11:52.912+09:00">they are ready to be ruined for one,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.102" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:12:12.844+09:00">and as a result one can survive together with them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.103" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:12:46+09:00">Now the general being prepared to face danger for one</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_002-11a.104" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-05-06T19:13:38.195+09:00">and as a result one can be safe together with him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_001-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-10T17:56:45.448+09:00">together they constitute one thing.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0904_CHANT_008-9a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-05T01:29:58.931+09:00">Words and actions embracing the One Unity is called morality.</seg>
                </p>
